{"type": "article", "id": 27288, "title": "3D 打印巧克力机", "description": "", "date": "2016-05-25T06:32:05Z", "super_tag": "", "tags": [], "category": 25, "column": 28, "author": 400262, "comment_count": 0, "praise_count": 66, "image": "img/article/article_show/20160702162507H2Sslo0aFB83wMq4.jpg", "contents": "\n\n<p>          </p>\n<p>3D 打印技术很常见，但你见过用它做食物的吗？荷兰设计工作室 <a href=\"http://www.michielcornelissen.com/\">Michiel Cornelissen Ontwerp</a> 最近就推出了一款比较特殊的 3D 打印机，使用巧克力作为“墨水”，帮助人们在家轻松实现 DIY 巧克力的梦想。这款名为 <a href=\"http://www.michielcornelissen.com/portfolio_page/xoco-chocolate-printer/\">XOCO</a> 的打印机采用了透明的玻璃罩，给人一种童话里出现的小工坊的感觉。用户通过配套的手机应用自定义巧克力的形状后就很直观地看到制作的全过程，底部的 LED 光环还可以显示过程的进度。</p>\n<div class=\"com-insert-images medium-insert-active medium-insert-images-wide\">\n<figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/201607021625046XO2BqopYJD4cndu.jpg\" alt=\"\" class=\"medium-insert-image-active\" data-ratio=\"0.63833333\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n<figcaption class=\"medium-insert-caption-placeholder\"></figcaption></figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160702162505vmMdxcWYz09ZJPAf.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.0\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160702162505CzHxu3ipWtsjZ42k.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.7\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160702162506pnwuYs4GLIcXqbON.gif\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.625\" data-format=\"gif\">\r\n</figure>\n</div>\n\n\n"}